NEOVIM TUTOR CHO SETUP CUA BAN
================================

Muc tieu cua file nay
---------------------

Day la tai lieu hoc Neovim theo cach thuc dung hang ngay, dua tren keymap va plugin
dang co trong config cua ban. Neu ban moi dung Vim/Neovim, hay di tu Phan 1 den
Phan 5. Neu da quen Vim, hay doc nhanh cac phan keybind rieng cua setup nay.

Quy uoc:
- <leader> trong config cua ban la phim Space.
- Khi tai lieu ghi <leader>ff nghia la bam Space roi bam f roi bam f.
- Normal mode la che do di chuyen va ra lenh.
- Insert mode la che do go chu.
- Visual mode la che do chon vung.
- Command mode la che do go lenh bat dau bang :.


PHAN 1: TU DUY VIM/NEOVIM
-------------------------

Neovim khong giong editor thong thuong. Ban lam viec bang cac che do:

- Normal: di chuyen, xoa, copy, tim kiem, goi LSP, mo file.
- Insert: nhap text.
- Visual: chon text roi thao tac.
- Command: chay lenh nhu :w, :q, :Lazy, :Mason.
- Terminal: tuong tac voi shell ben trong Neovim.

Nguyen tac quan trong:
- O Normal mode cang nhieu cang tot.
- Vao Insert mode de go, xong bam Esc de quay lai Normal.
- Ket hop operator + motion: d + w = xoa den tu tiep theo, c + i + w = doi ca tu.
- Dung text object de sua code nhanh: ci", ci), ci}, diw, yiw.


