PHAN 4.1: SEARCH AND REPLACE NHANH TRONG BUFFER
------------------------------------------------

Match.nvim dung cho search/replace nhanh trong buffer hien tai.
No khong thay the project-wide replace; khi can tim ca repo, dung Telescope live grep.

- <leader>Ms   Nhap search text roi mo Match UI.
  Dung khi muon search/replace mot pattern cu the trong file hien tai.

- <leader>Mw   Mo Match UI bang word duoi cursor.
  Dung khi muon doi nhanh bien/text dang dung tai cursor.

- <leader>Ml   Mo Match UI bang dong hien tai.
  Dung khi muon tim/replace ca line hien tai.

- <leader>MS   Mo Scooter replace TUI cho folder/project hien tai.
  Dung khi muon search/replace nhieu file co review tung match truoc khi apply.

Trong Match UI:
- <Tab>        Chuyen giua search va replace.
- <Up>/<Down>  Nhay qua match truoc/sau.
- <CR>         O search window: chuyen sang replace. O replace window: replace all.
- <C-u>        Undo replacement.
- <C-r>        Redo replacement.
- <Esc>/<C-q>  Dong UI.

Trong Scooter:
- Search text / Replace text: nhap noi dung tim va noi dung thay.
- Fixed strings: bat khi muon tim chu thuong, khong dung regex.
- Files to include/exclude: gioi han folder/file pattern can thay.
- Chon tung match de apply khi muon thay an toan tren nhieu file.


PHAN 5: LSP VA IDE WORKFLOW
---------------------------

LSP giup Neovim co tinh nang IDE: go to definition, hover, rename, code action,
diagnostic, symbol search, inlay hints.

Keymap LSP chinh:

- K            Hover documentation.
  Dung khi muon xem type/doc cua symbol duoi con tro.

- Gd           Go to definition.
  Dung khi muon nhay den noi dinh nghia.

- GD           LSP finder.
  Dung khi muon xem definition/references/implementation theo UI cua Lspsaga.

- Gp           Peek definition.
  Dung khi muon xem dinh nghia ma khong roi file hien tai.

- gr           References/finder.
  Dung khi muon xem cac noi su dung symbol.

- gI           Go to implementation.
  Dung voi interface/type/class co implementation.

- <leader>la   Lspsaga code action.
  Dung de quick fix, organize import, generate missing code, fix lint voi UI cua Lspsaga.

- <leader>lA   Native LSP code action.
  Dung khi muon goi truc tiep vim.lsp.buf.code_action, hoac khi can so sanh voi Lspsaga.

- <leader>lc   Color presentation.
  Dung khi cursor nam tren ma mau va muon chon format hien thi cua mau do.

- <leader>lr   Rename symbol.
  Dung khi doi ten bien/function/class an toan trong project.

- <leader>lf   Format file/vung chon.
  Dung khi muon format thu cong.

- <leader>lF   Toggle autoformat.
  Dung khi project khong muon format on save tam thoi.

- <leader>li   LspInfo.
  Dung de check file hien tai co LSP nao attach.

- <leader>lR   Restart LSP.
  Dung khi LSP bi treo, mat diagnostic, root sai.

- <leader>lh   Toggle inlay hints.
  Dung khi muon hien/an type hints, parameter hints.

- <leader>lo   Code outline.
  Dung de xem structure file: class, function, method.

- <leader>lp   Preview code action.
  Dung khi muon xem preview/diff cua code action truoc khi apply.

- <leader>lI   Incoming calls.
  Dung de xem ai goi function hien tai.

- <leader>lO   Outgoing calls.
  Dung de xem function hien tai goi nhung gi.

- <leader>lj   Next diagnostic.
  Dung de nhay den loi/canh bao tiep theo.

- <leader>lk   Previous diagnostic.
  Dung de quay lai loi/canh bao truoc.

- <leader>ll   Toggle code lens.
  Dung khi code lens lam roi mat hoac can bat lai.

- <leader>ls   Buffer symbols.
  Dung de tim symbol trong file hien tai.

- <leader>lS   Workspace symbols.
  Dung de tim symbol trong toan project.

- <leader>lm   Mason Installer.
  Dung de cai LSP/formatter/linter/debugger.

Keymap LSP native co the co san trong Neovim moi:
- gra          Code action native.
- grn          Rename native.
- grr          References native.
- gri          Implementation native.
- grt          Type definition native.
- gO           Document symbols native.
- ]d / [d      Next/previous diagnostic.
- ]D / [D      Next/previous ERROR diagnostic.

Khi nao dung LSP workflow:
- Muon hieu code: K, Gd, gr, <leader>lo.
- Muon sua code an toan: <leader>lr, <leader>la.
- Muon debug LSP: <leader>li, <leader>lR, :Mason, :checkhealth.


