PHAN 26: CAU TRUC CONFIG HIEN TAI
---------------------------------

Nguyen tac maintain config:

- init.lua chi require cac module boot chinh.
- lua/core/ chua hanh vi core cua editor: globals, env, options, filetype, autocmds, commands.
- lua/config/ chua config chia se cho plugin/ecosystem: lazy.nvim, LSP helper, icons.
- lua/plugins/ chua plugin specs, tach theo domain: ai, completion, dap, database, editor, git, langs, lsp, navigation, sessions, terminal, testing, ui, writing.
- ftplugin/ chua setting va keymap rieng theo filetype.
- snippets/ chua snippet tu chinh ban viet.

Quy uoc vua refactor:

- lua/core/options.lua la noi dat option core cua Neovim.
- lua/core/autocmds.lua chi nen giu autocmd cross-filetype/cross-editor.
- ftplugin/qf.lua quan ly quickfix window va phim q de close.
- ftplugin/markdown.lua, text.lua, log.lua, gitcommit.lua quan ly wrap/spell.
- ftplugin/OverseerList.lua quan ly UI cua OverseerList.
- Dashboard alpha-nvim load bang VimEnter, khong con nam trong nhom startup plugin.
- tree-sitter-norg va tree-sitter-norg-meta chi load khi dung Neorg/.norg.
- Catppuccin tat default_integrations va chi bat integration dang dung hang ngay de giam startup cost.
- lazy.nvim tat pkg scan, rocks scan, local .lazy.lua spec va change detection de giam spec-evaluation cost.
- GraphQL LSP chi attach vao file .graphql/.gql va project co graphql config/schema, tranh chay trong moi file JS/TSX.

Khi them config moi:

- Neu la option cho moi file: lua/core/options.lua.
- Neu la rule detect filetype: lua/core/filetype.lua truoc, chi dung ftdetect/ khi can Vimscript-style detection.
- Neu la setting theo ngon ngu/filetype: ftplugin/<filetype>.lua.
- Neu la plugin: lua/plugins/<domain>/<plugin>.lua.
- Neu la helper dung lai nhieu noi: lua/core/utils.lua hoac tach ve lua/utils/ khi file bat dau lon.


